Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.87,0:03:55.05,Default - italics,miya,0000,0000,0000,,Được đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.05,0:03:57.28,Default,nozaki,0000,0000,0000,,Năm phút sau khi gửi tin...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.28,0:03:58.30,SignA,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\p1\c&HFFFFFF&\frz15.85\fscx345\fscy106\pos(868.070984,890.570984)}m 0 0 l 150 0 150 150 0 150{\p0}
