Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.37,0:04:00.55,Default - italics,miya,0000,0000,0000,,Tôi sẽ duyệt lại.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.55,0:04:03.55,Default,nozaki,0000,0000,0000,,Và chỉ 1 phút sau khi tôi gọi ảnh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.55,0:04:04.55,SignA,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\p1\c&HFFFFFF&\frz15.85\fscx345\fscy106\pos(868.070984,890.570984)}m 0 0 l 150 0 150 150 0 150{\p0}
